metadata.name: Magic tree
metadata.description:
Sofiyivsky Park, Uman, Ukraine. The small island looking like a natural natural tree from above. From collection "My magical Ukraine".
 In March 2022, my printed photo book "Ukraine you have never seen before" was supposed to be published. But the treacherous war of Russia against my country destroyed not only houses and people. It kill my unborned book too. In this NFT collection, I will give life to the unborned pieces which should have been published.

1/1 Edition, Digital Photograph
Collection: My magical Ukraine
Artist: Yevhen Samuchenko (Q-lieb-in)
Achievements: HIPA Gold Medal,  has been featured
